STATE EX REL. DAVIS
v.
GHIZ 2019-0921 Supreme Court of Ohio. September 4, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

Appellant has not filed a merit brief, due August 26, 2019, in compliance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio and therefore has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Cause dismissed.
